    "Table 5.6: Sample parameters for CGGI and DM.",
    "The first two parameter sets for CGGI (with n = 742 and 777) are taken from the TFHE-rs library 15.",
    "The third and fourth parameter sets (with n = 805 and 687) are from the Concrete compiler.",
    "The fourth (with n = 503) and fifth (with n = 556) parameter sets are taken from the parameters recommended for the CGGI implementation in OpenFHE v1.2.0 [MP21, BBB + 22].",
    "Finally, the sixth (with n = 447) and seventh (with n = 593) correspond to the parameters recommended for the DM implementation in OpenFHE v1.2.0 [LMK + 23, BBB + 22]."
